Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.13,0:22:18.69,ED-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不胜枚举
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.91,0:22:22.30,ED-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}若你的眼神在呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.50,0:22:26.36,ED-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我便靠本能来判断
