Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.86,0:22:33.60,ED-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}光明与黑暗 相随相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.60,0:22:37.54,ED-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}仿若珍珠 连成一串
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.54,0:22:41.55,ED-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}自有缘由
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.28,0:22:46.00,ED-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}偶然也好 自然也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.00,0:22:50.72,ED-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}终将化作期待的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.77,0:22:54.44,ED-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}心的温度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.56,0:22:57.29,ED-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}开始渐渐上升
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.42,0:23:01.30,ED-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没有伪装 亦无需试探
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.30,0:23:05.86,ED-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}做最真的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.06,0:23:09.84,ED-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}坚守信仰 不离不弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.84,0:23:13.45,ED-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好想告诉你
